{
  "stem": "8947.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Auschwitz, it was a terrible in-- incident that it's-- it's in my mind.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was very lucky on that day because I could have been killed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, we had-- we had very little water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And thirst is horrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sometimes it can be worse than hunger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then there were these guards, coming on a truck with these big containers of water, you know, carrying.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they came through our camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember something-- I was very thirsty, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I saw that still there is humaneness in this guard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Mostly were SS.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Wehrmacht-- there were some Wehrmacht guards, who were-- had some-- who some more humaneness.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But this is was a short, little guy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was riding that thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I speak German, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went and I ask him if I can have a little water.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was naive, maybe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was 18 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, because I did it, you know-- so all the others were coming and begging him for water, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And naturally, he-- he started going with his truck-- he-- naturally he didn't give you the water.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He started going with his truck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then, as he was going, you know, water was dripping, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That same container was the moving, you know, back and forth, and some water was dripping on the ground.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "People were running to lick that water, and from the exhaust pipe, the water that just trickled down, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then, he was very upset that any water is-- is-- we are not going to have any water.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He said, you want water?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he started you know-- he started to beat some who were close.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then he put his truck.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
